NODE STRUCTURE

     +----+<---TEMPLATE
     |node|<---MOUSE HANDLERS
     |    |<---INTERFACE RENDERER
     +----+<---RECALCULATION FUNCTION

NODE PROGRAMS

   - add new template id to the ../node_resource_ids.h header

   - create a recalculation function (node_recalc.c)

   - create a template (node_templates.c) where you bind the recalculator and
     configure inputs/outputs/labels

   - add template to the node_mapper_create_template list in node_templates.c

NODE INTERFACES

   - in the template you can bind an interface

   - interfaces are defined in ../../user/editrs/node_interaction

   - add EXPORT_INTERFACE({interface_name}) to node_interaction.h

   - implement interface (e.g. node_interface_MAPPER.c )

   - bind interface in node_interaction.c: initNodeDispatcher() with 
     IMPORT_INTERFACE macro

   - if the node interface renders anything to the screen, add in 
     nodeMapEditor.c:render_node_gui  with the RENDERABLE_INTERFACE macro

